             was indicted, for that <rs id="t17840707-116-off564" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17840707-116-off564" type="offenceCategory" value="deception"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17840707-116-off564" type="offenceSubcategory" value="fraud"></interp>
               he being a profligate person, on the <rs id="t17840707-116-cd565" type="crimeDate">17th of June</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17840707-116-off564 t17840707-116-cd565"></join> did falsly pretend to 
                     <persName id="t17840707-116-person1179">
                        Owen
                         Owens
                     <interp inst="t17840707-116-person1179" type="surname" value="Owens"></interp>
