                     </persName>
                   servant to 
                     <persName id="t17840707-116-person1180">
                        Samuel
                         Shepherd
                     <interp inst="t17840707-116-person1180" type="surname" value="Shepherd"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17840707-116-person1180" type="given" value="Samuel"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17840707-116-person1180" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     </persName>
                  , Esq; in the Middle Temple, that he was sent to Mr. Shepherd, from Mr. Clermont's for Burn's Justice or Compton's Practice meaning certain books, by which he obtained the same books, value 10 s. the property of the said 
                     
                        <persName id="t17840707-116-victim1182" type="victimName">
                           Samuel 
                           Shepherd
                        <interp inst="t17840707-116-victim1182" type="surname" value="Shepherd"></interp>
